Dialogs.Dialog: (I know！ Maybe I should invite Rinko-chan to the Nikko/Kinugawa trip sweepstakes...)
Say, can I ask you a thing ▲小早川＊▲？
Actually, you know, I won again, a travel sweepstakes.
What's the matter... aren't you happy？
I may have said this before, but you're buying those, right？ Geez, it's obvious.
That's not true！ And this time, it's not Atami, it's "Adult School Trip to Nikko/Kinugawa hot springs, 2 days and 1 night"！！
I see～ Nikko/Kinugawa... huh？ "Adult school trip"？
Well, in our case, the school trip is just for students as it is. A trip is a trip, yeah？
Right？ And it's free, you know？
I don't mean it that way.
You idiot！ It's the "school trip" part, okay.
Eh, something about the fact that this trip doesn't match your style, ▲小早川＊▲？
Yeah, but... it's not a bad thing to go？ For a real school trip with you...
I get it. Well, we're in different grades, right？
It's a different story if you want to repeat a year.
Don't be so blunt... but yes, that's what it means, isn't it？
Yes... that's it... yes, yes. Hehehe...
Nothing？ And then？ When？ If it's my day off, any day is fine with me, okay？
Let's see, we'll set a date...
Then, from ▲月▲▲日▲, a one-night, two-day adult school trip！
I mean, you know... This has nothing to do with "adults", you know？ Let me tell you now, we're students, you and Rinko.
Well... I don't mind if we act as adults a little bit. You know, we're alone, right？ Rinko's your girlfriend, yeah？
(All right！！ It's just us going on a school trip, ▲小早川＊▲！)
Actually, I won it again. Our Adult School Trip to Nikko/Kinugawa.
No, no, no... can't, can't, can't.
I won it！ So you're not going to go？
I didn't say that, though. You're not fooling me, are you？ Like a riddle seminar at the place I went to. You seem like the type of person who would target me...
You're overthinking it... More importantly, the schedule, what do you want to do？
(We'll have to set up a date for later...)
All right！ Let's go on an "Adult school Trip" for two days and one night on ▲月▲▲日▲！
Don't stress the 'adult' part. It's just a small part.
I see... How much is a small part？
(I get to go on a school trip alone with you again ▲小早川＊▲！)
(I know！ Maybe I should invite Rinko-chan again to travel to Nikko/Kinugawa...)
Do you need to do any shopping？ You know, for the school trip？
You should think about that. You're older than me.
I thought that was the case. Well, for starters...
(Wait... we are going to Kinugawa hot springs, so again, there might be a family bath or something like that...)
Don't you need to buy a swimsuit, ▲小早川＊▲？
Swimsuit？ At this time of the year？
Look, there might be family baths again, like in Atami, you know？
I know there might be, but why are you assuming that I'm going to go in...
I didn't say so, but... somehow, I mean, it's embarrassing to be in a swimsuit together...
...Eh？ Don't you mean without a swimsuit？
Finally！ Is that it for shopping？ What did you buy, ▲小早川＊▲？
Oh, snacks... Well, they're a bit like a school trip, though, so it's fine.
Well, when you're used to traveling as much as Rinko is, it means you don't have to be particularly prepared.
Then why did we come here to shop...？
Why not, if you're all set？ Rinko has her full confidence in you.
See you later, okay？ Pack the night before so you don't get swamped on the day of the trip, okay？
Yes, yes. I will do my best！ Well, bye-bye！
(Hah～... I'm sleepy... Um, I wonder where you are, ▲小早川＊▲.)
(Not here yet... well, that's to be expected？)
(Hey now... this is past fashionably late...)
I aced it, you say... did you sleep in？
I was preparing last night like you said, and it got late.Have I done well？
Well, yeah. No wonder you overslept.
Well, you'll just have to tolerate it in light of this beautiful May weather, won't you！
Didn't I tell you to get ready before you went to bed？
Now, now, girls have a lot going on. See, you know what they say about a maiden's heart and the autumn sky, right？
Well na... no, that's totally unrelated.
Hehe！ Come, shall we go？ Let's go on a school trip！
Hey, hey, aren't we going to transfer some place？
Yeah, in the Tobu Railway express from Asakusa.
And when we get on that express, what then？
We're going to Kinugawa hot springs, aren't we？
No, stay in Kinugawa today, and tomorrow we will―― you haven't seen our tour itinerary at all, ▲小早川＊▲？
Oh... the limited express Spacia, huh...
Heh... feels like a school trip. Looks like it's going to fly, right？
I don't think it'll fly, though. Looks fast, though.
Come on, let's get in！ Rinko wants the window side！
I remember now. Have you seen the tour itinerary, ▲小早川＊▲？
Yeah！ I haven't seen it at all.
That's a man's chance to show off, isn't it？ Rinko's going to take three steps back and be the woman who follows. I'm counting on you▼
(I don't think that's what you meant...)
Oh, the Spacia is already here！
Well, it's time for the school trip to begin！
Ugh... something makes me feel bloated before I get on the express.
You have a warrior's tremor？ I can get that！
Wait, go ahead and sit down first... Oh, Rinko wants the window side！
(You can either go to the bathroom or... take three steps back...)
Hmm... spacious interior, big chairs！ I knew the express was good！
I knew it, the Spacia is incredible. I bought coffee and potato chips at the buffet.
The buffet is great, but are you sure you're ready to eat that now？
I'm fine. I mean, let me tell you something, it's a school trip. Do you understand？
I mean, you and Rinko are in the same grade, right？ Don't you remember that？
Don't be too bossy, even though you're a boy of my grade. Understand？
Oh... the scenery is very different when you get to this area...
What can I do about being in the same grade？ Specifically.
You're still thinking about that... well... like the way you talk？
Right？ That's what I was simulating in my mind...
Saying thanks doesn't feel quite the same as usual...
In your case, I guess so, ▲小早川＊▲...
Why don't we change the characters？ For example, a nice guy and a cute girl, like a couple in a Showa-era youth drama.
(Being in the same grade seems no longer relevant...)
If I said "Rinko-chan will act honest and cute once more"... would you be happy？
Oh, sounds nice！ By all means！
(This is going to be another fun ride！)
We will soon arrive at Kinugawa hot spring. Please make sure that you do not forget anything...
And we arrived to Kinugawa hot springs... It's quite modern, isn't it？
Yeah... but when it's just the two of us, it's just that much more romantic... isn't it？
Stop for a moment... I told you！ You must act as a nice guy！
Yeah, let's make lots of great memories, ▲小早川＊▲！
Stop, stop. Um... yes, I see, I see, that's right. Okay, um... no, you better act normal.
Hey, what's that statue？ I wonder if it's an ogre... Cute▼ Shall we go see it？
We're here together again, aren't we？ Here, at the Kinugawa hot springs...
Yeah, another night at Kinugawa, right？
Yup. Even though we'll be together all day... makes me a little nervous.
It's okay！ I won't do anything strange.
Yeah... but just a little's fine... nope, it's nothing！
(This is nice. This doesn't look like a school trip, though.)
Oh, no problem... for now, let's go down to the riverbank where the boarding area is located.
The water is clear... so beautiful...
Yeah, sure... I mean, really, are you going to stick with that？
You know life jackets？ In terms of size, do you think one made for a 4 years old elementary school student will fit you, ▲小早川＊▲？
Oh, I think the boarding has started！ Shall we go？
Thank you！ Let's go to the river, shall we？
Hah～！ The air is nice and chilly...
Yeah... and the flow is slow around here, right？
At this point, they had no idea that it was going to be a jungle cruise full of ferocious beasts... hehehe！
Sorry to keep you waiting！ We're ready to board！
Ah, hurry up！ Rinko wants to be in the front！ Let's go！
Oh... it's more thrilling than I thought...
Yes, here comes the water！ Please stand up！
Yes, this is the Haunted Rock！ It looks haunted～.
Hahaha！ That's too much to ask！ I mean, gorilla rock, elephant rock, and jungle rock were all there before！
Yes, please raise from your seats！
Oh... that's a lot of water！
Yeah！ Rinko is safe, right！ Hehe！
Yes, look over there！ Do you see that protruding rock？
Yeah, I see it！ That's a gorilla！
Yeah, I've decided. I'll quit. I can't do it. I can't be a cute girl in the Showa era. First of all, I can't do the lines.
That was quick... Well, keep doing as usual.
Right？ But you know... hey, it was fun, being an honest character.
So... the honest and cute Rinko-chan, will keep going... yes？
Next up, a bus ride to Tobu World Square！
No～, that was so fun！ That was entertaining, isn't it？
The boatman's narration worked, didn't it？
That's what I'm talking about！ I know... hey, hey, can I hold your hand？
Hehe♪ And all the way on the bus, too, yeah？
Oh, here comes the bus！ Well, shall we go？ To Tobu World Square！
Rinko was looking forward to this place quite a bit.
When I was little, I had a lot of dolls and dollhouses, and I used to play a lot with Mama.
(I'm sure you're talking about your late mother...)
They made me wear all these frilly clothes and my hair was long... I can't imagine what it must be like now, can I？
That's nice. Today, you're honest and cute, right, ▲小早川＊▲？
Tobu World Square entrance. Please make sure not to forget anything when you get off...
We arrived. Tobu World Square, huh...
"The encounter of Dreams and Emotions". I'm so stoked... is that okay？ Rinko's getting her hopes up, okay？
Tobu World Square entrance. Please make sure not to forget anything when you get off...
We're here！ Tobu World Square, the encounter of Dreams and Emotions...
Eh～ I'm going to go ahead and say this now, Rinko's going back to her childhood.
That's a lot of excitement, though.
Oh, the world at a 1/25th scale...
Yes... hmmm, wait a minute！ Even the people are well made. That's so exciting▼
Ah, over there！ Look, come here！
Look, look！ Look at all the little people walking around and shopping！
Yay, little people！ I feel like a giant monster！
Come on, take a photo！ Gyaooo！！
Oh, this is Europe, isn't it？
Yeah！ Around Europe in an instant！
Don't run too fast and make a mistake, okay, ▲小早川＊▲？
Hehe！ Ah, I can see the Buckingham Palace in London！ And there's the Arc de Triomphe！
Even at 1/25th the size, it's pretty big, isn't it？ Rinko can go through it, you know？
You can't do that, can you？ Or, you should not do that？
That's what it is, isn't it？ That's what you call pretending, isn't it？ Okay...
What is it you're looking for？
Well... ah！ I think that's it！
Hah... I knew it, I like it. I want to keep looking at it...
Neuschwanstein Castle... You like it a lot, don't you？
Yeah... because it's the most beautiful castle in the world, you know？
I bet under this roof is the Great Hall, where they have a ball every night...
When I was little, I used to play ball with my mom...
Wearing a princess dress... of course, it's for a toy. But you can also put dresses on your dolls...
I had a great time... but――.
I still feel a little lonely...
Hah... Tobu World Square is nice！ Feels like I've been around the world！
Yeah. You know, isn't Rinko getting a little too excited？
Hmm... is it too weird？ Should I be acting normal？
That kind of thing is okay. It's a school trip, right？
The cute and honest Rinko-chan will do something like that！
Come on, shall we go？ The bus will be here soon.
That's right！ Our next stop, EDO WONDERLAND, in Nikko Edomura！
Hah... I'm happy this time too！
Hehe, yeah？ Miniatures are kind of, you know, exciting.
You like this kind of thing, don't you, ▲小早川＊▲？
It's just the two of us on a school trip, with the honest and cute Rinko-chan. Hehe...
This is the entrance to EDO WONDERLAND Nikko Edomura. Please make sure not to forget anything when you get off...
Oh... here we are... EDO WONDERLAND Nikko Edomura.
EDO WONDERLAND... Looks like the entrance to a temple―― ah！
Some kind of crazy-looking bureaucrat is looking over here...
Sir, do you have a bill of passage？
Yes？ Um... eh？ Bill of passage？
Oh, I see！ Let's see, two adult tickets-de gozaru！
...yes, indeed！ Well then, have a safe trip-de gozaru！
Oh, that kind of cold attitude is not good-de gozaru？ Hmm？
Oh, that's right... I see that-de gozaru！
Hehe！ Now, off we go-de gozaru！
This is the entrance to EDO WONDERLAND Nikko Edomura. Please make sure not to forget anything when you get off...
Oh... EDO WONDERLAND of Nikko Edomura.
We're here again-de gozaru. Hey, the bill of passage！ Give me, give me！
Just so you know, Rinko is a hardcore go-home club member, so I'm rather familiar with period dramas.
This is amazing... hmm？ Is that a "Yaba"！ So reliable！
No, it's quite difficult, isn't it？
You put a little too much effort in this, onii-san？ Want to give it a try, onee-san？
Just leave it to me！ Rinkonosuke will avenge you-de gozaru！
Yeah！ I got a stuffed animal-de gozaru～▼
Hmm？ Something smells good, doesn't it？
Come to think of it, it's already past noon, right？
You can't fight a war on an empty stomach-de gozaru！ Let's go！
All right, I'll have the eel kamameshi！ Hey, you still haven't decided yet, ▲小早川＊▲？
Please wait a moment-de gozaru... Okay, then, kare-rice！
It's "kare-rice"-de gozaru. Rinkonosuke is conservative in this way-de gozaru.
That procession is... the "Ninja Raven House", huh.
"Ninja"？ Fufufu... this makes my arm tremble-de gozaru.
Eh... you can't be serious, can you？ Wait, wait, Rinkonosuke-dono！
No-Nothing？ It's just that ninjas were popping out of strange places...
Awesome, that was some serious action, wasn't it？
Well, I'll leave it at that for today-de gozaru...
Oh, look over there. That black wall.
The "Ninja Karakuri Proverb Maze", huh... are you sure it's okay？
Hmm？ I've been looked down once... a race, off I go！
Huh？ I think I saw "Curse a man, and you'll get two holes"...
It's too hard... Hey, how's it going over there, ▲小早川＊▲？
Hehe！ I'm already by the finish line！
I'm finally here！ Huh, what's up, where are you, ▲小早川＊▲？
Did you notice the hidden door？ You'll have to go through, okay, ▲小早川＊▲！？
I guess that was a bad idea...
Hey～！ See that escape hatch on the way out？ Use it to get out！
I should go pick you up...
I'm heading there... where are you？ Hey, Rinkonosuke.
I see. All right, let's go to the finish line, okay？
Here we are！ Come on, go ahead, get it！
Wait, I'm really glad you didn't forget about the honest Rinko-chan.
The Oiran road trip is about to begin. Both of you, please take a look at Oiran's graceful "Oneri"！
Hah... I want to walk around like that... I know it doesn't look good on me, you know？
Maybe it's not true, you know？
You're lying. You really think it's going to be like Shichigosan, don't you？
You know, earlier, Rinko forgot something again.
Even if Rinko is in the Oiran and looks like a Shichigosan, will you be my only customer？
(Okay, I've seen all the souvenir shops... Huh, where's ▲小早川＊▲？)
Sorry to keep you waiting. I bought a katana and a bunch of other stuff. And... ta-da！
Strap？ Ah, it has our names...
The one with "Rinko" on it is yours, right？ They're matching, you know？
Wow, that doesn't sound a bit like you, does it, ▲小早川＊▲？
It's okay, that's the kind of Rinko I'm today.
I see... a memento of the honest and cute Rinko-chan, right？
Yes. It's a memento... And while you're at it, think of it as a Rinko and take good care of it▼
I'm a little embarrassed, but I'll treasure it.
Hah... it was fun being in EDO WONDERLAND Nikko Edomura. I feel like I haven't played enough yet.
Hah～～ I player too much- de gozaru...
Haha, you were really excited, weren't you, ▲小早川＊▲？
Hehe, I guess？ It's okay, today！
You're the honest and cute Rinko-chan, aren't you？
Yeah, it's a school trip, right？
Oh yeah, because after this, we're finally going to the ryokan！
(I didn't want it to sound weird...)
You want to go to bed, I get it... we had a lot of fun today...
I don't want to go to bed yet... don't act like you are my Papa and I'm your kid.
Well, the bus to the hotel is... ah, it's that one！
Thank you for your patience. Guests, we have arrived to Kinugawa Plaza Hotel！
Here we are！ So this is today's lodging, the Kinugawa Plaza Hotel！
I see！ It's gorgeous... I mean, what is that？ ...a ball？
Sorry to keep you waiting. I just checked in, okay？ Dinner's at 7:00 pm.
That's not what I'm talking about... is it okay？ Isn't it kind of too gorgeous？ Oh, actually, it's an extra charge！
Thank you for waiting. Let me show you to your room. Miss, where is your luggage？
Understood. Now, please come this way.
Hmmm... I guess I don't look like a wife, huh？ Well, it's okay, isn't it？
Thank you for your patience. Guests, we have arrived to Kinugawa Plaza Hotel！
Here we are！ Kinugawa Plaza Hotel！
I'll be under your care once more！ Hehe！
Sorry to keep you waiting. I just checked in. Dinner is at 7:00 pm.
Seven o'clock？ Okay！ Oh, here comes the attendant！ Ahem！
It's a nice hotel, isn't it, Dear？
Thank you for waiting. Let me show you to your room. Ma'am, would you like me to bring your luggage？
Um... it's okay. My husband will carry it.
Now, please make yourself at home.
It's spacious... I mean, it's huge！ The TV is huge！
True. The interior is stylish, too... They have massage chairs, too, you know？
Rinko's getting more and more scared... It's okay, right？ It's free, right？
Okay！ Come on, let's have fun in this gorgeous room！
Come, Rinko will make you some tea.
But still, it's a great room... You can see the Kinugawa River clearly.
And it has its own private outdoor bath on the balcony, right？
Yeah！ As you can see. I can't get in there, though.
Because you can see everything from inside the room！
But, you see, there are shoji screens, so you can't even see――
I don't know if I can trust you.
Hey, before we eat, do you want to go to the public bath？
Well, I'll meet you here, okay？
Girls are fine！ See you later.
A "treasure hot spring"！ That's good luck！
So spacious！ Overlooking the Kinugawa River！ Feels so good！
(Hah... I can get rid of the tiredness of the day... I feel sleepy...)
Okay, it's time to go up！
That was dangerous... I really have to go out.
That's nice, it looks good on you.
Uh... those massage chairs are so nice！ Rinko's house needs one of those too.
That much？ Should I try them？
Excuse me. I am here to prepare your meal.
Is this Kaiseki？ Look at the "Oshinagaki".
Oh, looks like there's plenty more on the way, huh？
Rinko can't have it all. Um... then... okay！
Sashimi and... paste？ And I'll give you some hot pot, and you can have all the desserts.♪
Now, now. In exchange, Rinko will feed them to you.
Do you want to digest our food and explore inside the hotel？
Hmmm... I feel like lazing around, but... okay, I'll go.
There are various local specialties, Utsunomiya Gyoza, and many local limited edition confections...
Oh, did you find anything good to snack on later, ▲小早川＊▲？
I found some dumpling potato chips, yeah？ Is this local？
Do you mean Utsunomiya Gyoza？ Are you going to buy some？
I'll buy it, but I won't eat it, okay？ See... it's called etiquette.
Oh, I saw something earlier, like an arcade, you know？ Let's go！
Wow, they have billiards！ You want to play？
Well, playing billiards is a disadvantage――.
Oh, I see. Little people often can't reach the cue ball, can they？
Hehehe, my victory！ Don't ever call me a little person ever again.
It's a tough one, isn't it？ I thought I was at a disadvantage in a yukata because of the hem.
You forgot to pay attention to it halfway through！
Wait！ What are you looking at！ Lecher！
(I didn't meant to make it sound like that...)
I'm sweating... Rinko is going to the spa one more time, okay？
Oh, by the way, I got a ticket for a private bath. I think it was called "Oniton-tei".
Come on, put on your swimsuit, will you？
Well, since we're here... let's go.
Ah, come on, look！ Is that it？
Heh... isn't it nice？ Looks a little bit like a ghost lives there, doesn't it？
Well, yeah？ It's usually called elegance, right？ Let's go in！
Yeah, it's a nice feeling, but... I can hear the bugs...
Was that the honest you, ▲小早川＊▲？
Then, the honest and gentle Rinko-chan should wash your back？
...？ Come on, don't you want to go？
As I said！ Go ahead and get out！ I'm not getting dressed like this...
Hah～～！ School trips are the best！
It doesn't look like a school trip at all now, though, does it？
Well, it's a school trip for adults.
I'm starting to feel embarrassed... Don't look at me！
Sorry to keep you waiting, ▲主人公＊▲！
(Hmm！ I knew yukatas had a certain elegance to it...)
No, I just thought that wearing a yukata has a certain elegance to it, you know？
Thank goodness I didn't eat the potato chips earlier.
I thought maybe I'd do it one more time▼
Can I have a little bit of free time？ Until we get back to our rooms.
(I have nothing to do, I should go back to our room...)
I see... Oh, sorry, I have to go to the bathroom！
Hah... easy-going as ever, boys have it easier.
It's gorgeous, but it's missing something, you know？ A school trip feeling？
I knew it had to be this thing...
Did you get it？ School trip feeling？
Okay... I will consider that a declaration of war！
So, what do you want to do about our bed setting？
"What do I want to do"？ What do you mean？
I mean, you see, there are two beds, right？ An big ones to match.
Sure, it's a big bed, right？
Hey... that's wrong！ That's not what I meant！
What do you mean by that？
So, what Rinko means is, which bed do you want to use？ That's what she meant！
It's nothing！ Rinko wants the bed by the wall！
Rinko... should go to sleep too？
You know, Rinko forgot to tell you about this...
Speaking of school trips, besides the pillow fight, there's one more thing, right？
I don't think boys will do it, you know... saying who you like.
Rinko will tell you who she likes...
Hah！ I think it's time to go to bed！
*yawn*... Rinko will go to bed too...
You know, Rinko was thinking about this...
If you and Rinko had a real school trip, a real school trip, together...
Of course, our classmates would ask us questions, and the next day, they'd hoot and holler at us...
It's kind of nice, I kind of admire that kind of thing...
I feel like you and Rinko are the happiest people in the world right now.
*yawn*... sleepy. I guess I woke up a little too early...
(I woke up early and it paid off. I got a decent night's sleep last night！)
(Let's try not to wake her up...)
I might as well doodle on your sleepy face, something special of school trips.
You look so innocent... you're pretty cute, aren't you？
Good morning... did you just do something to me, ▲小早川＊▲？
Did she go somewhere else？ Are you there, ▲小早川＊▲？？
No way？ Hey, wait a minute！ I told you to stay in bed！
Anyway, she might be in trouble！
...sorry, I didn't realize you were in the middle of changing.
While you're sleeping, of course, so that you don't peek in on me.
I'm kidding♪ Breakfast is ready, let's go！
Oh... nice view！ And it smells great！
They've got all kinds of Japanese and Western food, you know？
Really？ Then let's go get some stuff！
Well, well, you've got a lot of food, huh？
Is that all you're going to eat for breakfast, ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko？ Rinko has her food on your tray, you know？
Thank you very much. We look forward to welcoming you again.
Okay... sorry for the wait, ▲小早川＊▲！
Nice hotel, wasn't it！ The "Kinugawa Plaza Hotel".
Yeah. It was a gorgeous school trip night.
I know, let's take a picture to commemorate the event, shall we？
All right！ Well then, today we're finally heading to Nikko！
Come on, hurry up！ We're not going to make it in time！
You bought too many souvenirs yesterday, didn't you？
Because if you don't buy a katana toy or something like that, you will definitely regret it later.
Rather, I think it's the other way around, usually...
Hah... glad we made it in time, huh？
Oh, the train is so short！ Heh, are we going to ride on this？
Which way to the front？ Rinko wants to be in the front！
Now, we change trains at Shimo-Imaichi and then Tobu Nikko Station. Let's go, shall we？
Hmm？ I was just saying goodbye to Kinugawa.
Yes. It was a lot of fun. See you later？ Like that.
Oh, the train is already coming！ I'll take the front seat！
Not that... I was just imagining...
When you come to an unfamiliar place like this, don't you imagine what it would be like？ Don't you imagine what it would be like if you lived here？
What would happen if you lived here...？
I bet we would ride this train together every day to school. We always have fixed seats and so on.
I get it... that kind of thing might be nice...
We're here！ Here we are, Nikko！
Here we are, Nikko... that's the Iroha slope, right？ The bus？ Let's go！
No, let's just drop our bags off somewhere first. It's heavy...
You're sloppy, aren't you？ Do you want Rinko to carry one for you？
Hehe, sorry▼ I'll go find a locker.
From Lake Chuzenji, it looks like Mt. Fuji...
As I said, if you look at it from above...
No. You don't understand at all.
We're here！ Now, let's drop our bags off and go to the bus stop, shall we？
Hah... that's where... the challenge of this school trip is.
I'm going to get sick. Just like a drunk.
Didn't you bring your sobriety pills？
I feel like I'm leaving my body... before I leave, Rinko'd like to give you a sermon.
I know！ Why don't we just climb up on foot？
No, no, no！ That's not possible...
Oh... that's indeed Iroha slope. I knew it would be like this...
